sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant A as AI Assistant
  participant G as Graphify CLI
  participant P as Parsers and Extractors
  participant O as graphify-out
  participant M as MCP or Query Layer

  U->>A: Ask codebase question or request /graphify
  A->>G: Trigger graph build or query path
  G->>P: Scan files and extract structure or semantics
  P-->>G: Nodes, edges, concepts
  G->>O: Write graph.html, GRAPH_REPORT.md, graph.json
  A->>M: Query graph for relevant context
  M->>O: Read graph artifacts
  O-->>M: Relevant subgraph or report context
  M-->>A: Compact evidence
  A-->>U: Answer with graph-assisted context

  Note over G,P: Based on README-level description; exact calls need source verification.

